Package: quartohelp
Type: Package
Title: Chat Interface to Quarto Documentation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    "Tomasz", "Kalinowski",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "tomasz@posit.co",
    comment = NULL
  )
Description: Launches an interactive chat app that retrieves and summarizes
    relevant Quarto documentation using both semantic and keyword-based search
    via an OpenAI-powered assistant. Returns authoritative excerpts, includes links
    to official resources, and helps users accomplish specific Quarto tasks quickly.
